ratings.comment: Tough lady, not very approachable outside of class.  Very defensive about the answers to her exams.  Much more entertaining than her coprofessor.  Do not be discouraged after the first exam; its still possible to get an A if you do well on the lab reports and seminar

Lazy professor who just sits in class and does nothing. extremely unhelpful. Fails to organize course properly and does not even know the lab notebook she issues to the class. Refers you to the TAs when you ask her for help. Does not care about students at all.
